Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:24.24,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}被悲伤浸染
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:28.72,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}肉体毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.51,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}填入绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:37.35,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}只剩下孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:43.40,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}只身的一人  终于和你相遇
